# PROJECT: PHANTOM
# Proportional-Navigation Heuristic Adaptive Missile-Tracking Nullification
# Author: Naresh Dama | March 2026 | Jacksonville, FL
# Target: IEEE TAES | Cursor + Python 3.11 | All phases use PHANTOM naming

## ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
## 1. PROJECT IDENTITY AND CONTEXT
## ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

This project implements a kinematically consistent missile guidance deception
system that exploits Extended Kalman Filter (EKF) chi-squared gating in
Proportional Navigation (PN)-guided missiles. The goal is simulation-validated
research suitable for IEEE TAES publication.

- Language: Python 3.11
- IDE: Cursor (VS Code-based)
- Research domain: Aerospace guidance, Electronic Warfare, Estimation Theory
- Target venue: IEEE Transactions on Aerospace and Electronic Systems (TAES)

## ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
